{"tid":1937730,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗又搞事，欺善怕惡既水晶姥姥帶頭搞k Kwong","createTime":"2020-03-22T06:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T06:06:26.000Z","uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"639381ea451fcf8c3fe547df8d8ff650bba6c11c","tid":1937730,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"之前水晶姥姥係倫敦人西先生個group講左柒野，俾人起底原來係雲粉就唔敢出po批鬥人<br />\n<br />\n依家見無人再搞佢，佢就繼續欺善怕惡，鬧k kwong叫人戴口罩有陰謀，出口罩賺錢唔啱<br />\n<br />\n最好一批免費口罩送去水晶姥姥屋企，咁佢就無聲出啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtBz3oY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtBz3oY.png&h=01fabb1c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}